Mini Project Question: E-Commerce Application (Java)

Design a Java-based E-Commerce application for an online shopping system.

Create a Product class with productId, productName, price, and stock.

Create a Customer class with customerId, name, and balance.

Implement a method to add products to a cart.

Use exception handling to manage out-of-stock products.

Create a custom exception InsufficientBalanceException.

Handle payment using try-catch-finally.

Display order confirmation on successful purchase.

Print meaningful error messages for failed transactions.

Ensure proper program termination without runtime errors.
